"The then National Senator for Citizen Unity Cristina Fernndez de Kirchner, at the presentation of his book ""Sinceramente"" in Rosario (Argentina), said that ""he does not regret the national channels, since otherwise the media would not have shown the public policies of the then President of Argentina""."
