"SKEPP is an independent Belgian skeptical organization. The organizations name is a backronym for ""Studiekring voor de Kritische Evaluatie van Pseudowetenschap en het Paranormale"" (""Study Circle for the Critical Evaluation of Pseudoscience and the Paranormal"")."
"SKEPP is a nonprofit organization emanated from the Belgian astronomical society, ""Vereniging voor Sterrenkunde"", and was founded in 1990 by, among others, Prof. Etienne Vermeersch, Prof. Willem Betz, Tim Trachet and Prof. Jean Paul Van Bendegem."
